                        Preliminary and Final Construction Documents. The improvements included replacement of
                        16-inch
                        and 30-inch
                        waterlines as well as 12-inch sanitary sewer line replacement and sewer line rehabilitation
                        (lining). Many of
                        the existing utilities are very old and were not documented or accurately mapped when
                        originally
                        constructed.
                        As such, PRC worked very closely with Wildcat Construction throughout the duration of the
                        project to address
                        unforeseen issues and to adjust designs when necessary.
                    </div>
